  "method": [
    "Add 1 tablespoon olive oil, heated on moderate in a big Dutch oven or",
    "large pot.",
    "Toss in the carrot, fennel, and fresh basil, and cook for a few minutes",
    "before adding the garlic.",
    "Boost the heat to medium and add the garlic broth and coriander",
    "seeds.",
    "Reduce to low heat and cook for 20 minutes, just until the rice is soft.",
